room_title: Escape room "Edmond's Attic" by Horror Escapes LA in Los Angeles
room_address: 1041 S. Olive St. Los Angeles, CA 90015
room_description: There's a vampire coven called The Count's Den where secrets are kept by a hunchbacked tongue-less servant named Edmond. Ava, a vampire to this coven has invited you to come to the coven and break into Edmond's attic apartment to see what secrets you can expose to her before Edmond returns. Edmond, being immortal also, is not the kindest servant. Hurry and assist Ava to break into the attic and get out before Edmond returns!
